com.interpss.core.aclf.adj

Interface PVBusLimit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfControlBus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RemoteQBus, StaticVarCompensator, SwitchedShunt
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PVBusLimitImpl, RemoteQBusImpl, StaticVarCompensatorImpl, SwitchedShuntImpl

    public interface PVBusLimit
extends AclfControlBus
    A representation of the model object 'PV Bus Limit'. PVBusLimit for GenPQ bus. Object id is the same as the busId it reference to. VSpec and QLimit are stored in the parent AclfBus object.
    See Also:
    AclfAdjustPackage.getPVBusLimit()
